Apakah begitu?  - Ya.

00:10:04.980 --> 00:10:06.314
Jadi suami..

00:10:06.689 --> 00:10:09.606
Bagaimana Anda
ingin merayakannya?

00:10:11.231 --> 00:10:13.231
Saya telah merencanakan kencan!

00:10:13.523 --> 00:10:14.731
Di luar rumah!

00:10:14.896 --> 00:10:16.147
Di teras!

00:10:17.106 --> 00:10:20.356
Tapi Anda harus mengenakan
pakaian kotor Anda!

